{
  "_comment": "Consumer-side cockpit view of the selfdef IPS CORE DETECTION STREAM \u2014 the daemon's central output (events seen on the bus, findings promoted by the correlator). Renders the selfdef-api /metrics counters: events/sec, findings/sec by severity, events/sec by class, and cumulative finding totals. The operator's at-a-glance 'is the IPS detecting + correlating?' view.",
  "annotations": {
    "list": []
  },
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 0,
  "id": null,
